  {
    "id": "748dae7f4b93b0a523926c65f0a6977e",
    "page_id": "p167304db9c48df1e72ed053b7771fb1",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "The Iron Commons — Ward Pemberton. Started this week; the chapters on grazing rights are excellent.",
    "order": "35",
    "created_time": "2026-02-05T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "25dee926f251e4fd3192da3dd94f96a3",
    "page_id": "p167304db9c48df1e72ed053b7771fb1",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "The Starling Effect — Jasmine Obi. Emma's pick. Finished it; the ending earned itself.",
    "order": "36",
    "created_time": "2026-02-06T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "8062226baed60af3c13f2167657c5db0",
    "page_id": "p167304db9c48df1e72ed053b7771fb1",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "The Warmth of Other Suns — Isabel Wilkerson. Rereading. Still the best narrative history I own.",
    "order": "37",
    "created_time": "2026-02-07T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "eb7bea6f44b5cf5f42718986b6e4d5bb",
    "page_id": "p167304db9c48df1e72ed053b7771fb1",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Grant — Ron Chernow. Slow first hundred pages, then it sings, as I told Lenny.",
    "order": "38",
    "created_time": "2026-02-08T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "3a288b8c25780637434c884a68598cd1",
    "page_id": "p167304db9c48df1e72ed053b7771fb1",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "A Sand County Almanac — Aldo Leopold. Annual reread. The land ethic still holds.",
    "order": "39",
    "created_time": "2026-02-09T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "c668148b03cf2720e2d171d9e1eaa02a",
    "page_id": "p167304db9c48df1e72ed053b7771fb1",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "The Control of Nature — John McPhee. For the lecture research.",
    "order": "40",
    "created_time": "2026-02-10T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "952413395959d9ace27bfac7512b0f9c",
    "page_id": "p167304db9c48df1e72ed053b7771fb1",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Desert Solitaire — Edward Abbey. Cranky and beautiful.",
    "order": "41",
    "created_time": "2026-02-11T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "4257e2133c80f238f6939b27c07c984e",
    "page_id": "p167304db9c48df1e72ed053b7771fb1",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "The Worst Hard Time — Timothy Egan. Dust Bowl policy failures, well told.",
    "order": "42",
    "created_time": "2026-02-12T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "bd9a8c95eb6707451c541e8ef4dc36e6",
    "page_id": "p4da19948f8a682fa70a6e1689d4381f",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Module 1 — Arrhenius calculated the greenhouse effect in 1896. Remarkable for the tools he had.",
    "order": "43",
    "created_time": "2026-02-13T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "d2e6e395828ddf48a913bda9e81675a7",
    "page_id": "p4da19948f8a682fa70a6e1689d4381f",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Module 3 — Industrial emissions and the early science. Callendar's 1938 paper is underrated.",
    "order": "44",
    "created_time": "2026-02-14T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "8f1bac986627380f5c35cc929c1efc8d",
    "page_id": "p4da19948f8a682fa70a6e1689d4381f",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Module 4 — The 1965 PSAC report warned of carbon dioxide. Nobody acted for decades.",
    "order": "45",
    "created_time": "2026-02-15T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "777b716c5420db97a7e57dcb9e022a0f",
    "page_id": "p4da19948f8a682fa70a6e1689d4381f",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Module 5 — Kyoto's structure vs. its enforcement. The gap is the whole story.",
    "order": "46",
    "created_time": "2026-02-16T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "971d12c2b34c6e5accd9ef10bac9ba6d",
    "page_id": "p4da19948f8a682fa70a6e1689d4381f",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Module 6 — Paris shifted to nationally determined contributions. Flexible, and therefore fragile.",
    "order": "47",
    "created_time": "2026-02-17T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "0332d463fb686ce8867f5eea52b8aa49",
    "page_id": "p4da19948f8a682fa70a6e1689d4381f",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Discussion post — patient, decades-long funding beats grand announcements. My old refrain.",
    "order": "48",
    "created_time": "2026-02-18T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "72acc4046d65b0d614625ddd5fdcbf60",
    "page_id": "p79649875dcb3d2b27d67c067700ff7f",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "CCC outline — Section 1: origins in 1933, relief and conservation joined.",
    "order": "49",
    "created_time": "2026-02-19T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "8f34e231073f289276364444b721ba08",
    "page_id": "p79649875dcb3d2b27d67c067700ff7f",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "CCC outline — Section 2: the camps in Maryland, Patapsco and Catoctin.",
    "order": "50",
    "created_time": "2026-02-20T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "597da72edf1203902f30a663b896272f",
    "page_id": "p79649875dcb3d2b27d67c067700ff7f",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "CCC outline — Section 3: the legacy in the state parks we still use.",
    "order": "51",
    "created_time": "2026-02-21T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "4cd0fae81f4da9f7ee76104491908ad0",
    "page_id": "p79649875dcb3d2b27d67c067700ff7f",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Open with the seawall — the audience knows that ground.",
    "order": "52",
    "created_time": "2026-02-22T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "4a7ef2394f4dc10e97aa0000968d31e1",
    "page_id": "p79649875dcb3d2b27d67c067700ff7f",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Close on stewardship as a long calendar, not a budget cycle.",
    "order": "53",
    "created_time": "2026-02-23T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "619d5fa4ec52ef32d6aa865883af073a",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Draft — the county stormwater fee is worth keeping; runoff into the Severn does not fix itself.",
    "order": "54",
    "created_time": "2026-02-24T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "2448d169e848359c6dbbb1602e620fe6",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Draft — public-lands budgets should be measured in decades, not appropriations.",
    "order": "55",
    "created_time": "2026-02-25T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "cb649ac79520bc08d26040d594153d1e",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Draft — a note of thanks to the library volunteers who keep the branch running.",
    "order": "56",
    "created_time": "2026-02-26T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "0005b64b7d40fef89f4451035c8b0204",
    "page_id": "p322a356e4524a1c92c2dc7c0dfabd8c",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Sighting — Northern cardinal, backyard feeder, first light. Safflower keeps the squirrels off.",
    "order": "57",
    "created_time": "2026-02-27T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "c391865e9e6db2dadd7e88c3fadfa914",
    "page_id": "p322a356e4524a1c92c2dc7c0dfabd8c",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Sighting — first junco of the winter. The cold is coming.",
    "order": "58",
    "created_time": "2026-02-28T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "19aa62074abcf19b822272ea93f1efd2",
    "page_id": "p322a356e4524a1c92c2dc7c0dfabd8c",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Sighting — Cooper's hawk cleared the feeder in one pass.",
    "order": "59",
    "created_time": "2026-03-01T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "3860d3fe3ec04274c08bc7060995f139",
    "page_id": "p322a356e4524a1c92c2dc7c0dfabd8c",
    "parent_block_id": "parent_block_id_000000",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Sighting — osprey back on the Severn nest platform. Spring at last.",
    "order": "60",
    "created_time": "2026-03-02T00:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-28T09:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
